trans-unit.source: Passed to custom WSDL exporters and importers to enable customization of the metadata export and import processes for a WSDL endpoint.
trans-unit.target: Passado para exporters WSDL personalizados e importadores para habilitar a personalização da exportação de metadados e importar os processos para um ponto de extremidade do WSDL.

trans-unit.source: The WsdlEndpointConversionContext class represents the context in which the custom WSDL for an endpoint is either exported using <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension?displayProperty=fullName> or imported using <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>.
trans-unit.target: A classe WsdlEndpointConversionContext representa o contexto no qual o WSDL personalizado para um ponto de extremidade é que um exportado usando <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>ou importados usando <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlImportExtension?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.IWsdlExportExtension?displayProperty=fullName>

trans-unit.source: The following properties enable you to retrieve the WSDL document object model for the current WSDL: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.ContractConversionContext%2A> property gets the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlContractConversionContext?displayProperty=fullName> for the endpoint contract.
trans-unit.target: As propriedades a seguir permitem que você recuperar o modelo de objeto do documento WSDL para o WSDL atual: - o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.ContractConversionContext%2A>propriedade obtém o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlContractConversionContext?displayProperty=fullName>para o contrato de ponto de extremidade.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlContractConversionContext?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.ContractConversionContext%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.Endpoint%2A> property gets the <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint?displayProperty=fullName> for the current endpoint.
trans-unit.target: -A <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.Endpoint%2A>propriedade obtém o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint?displayProperty=fullName>para o ponto de extremidade atual.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.ServiceEndpoint?displayProperty=fullName> </xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.Endpoint%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlBinding%2A> property gets the binding for the current endpoint.
trans-unit.target: -A <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlBinding%2A>propriedade obtém a associação para o ponto de extremidade atual.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlBinding%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlPort%2A> property gets the port for the current endpoint.
trans-unit.target: -A <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlPort%2A>propriedade obtém a porta para o ponto de extremidade atual.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.WsdlPort%2A>

trans-unit.source: - - The following methods enable you to add or remove custom WSDL elements to the appropriate scopes in the exported or imported WSDL: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultBinding%2A> method returns the fault binding for the specified fault.
trans-unit.target: – Os métodos a seguir permitem que você adicionar ou remover elementos WSDL personalizados para os escopos apropriados no WSDL exportado ou importado: - o <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultBinding%2A>método retorna a associação de falha para a falha específica.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultBinding%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultDescription%2A> method returns the fault for the specified fault binding.
trans-unit.target: -O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultDescription%2A>método retorna a falha para a associação de falha especificados.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetFaultDescription%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageBinding%2A> method returns the message binding for the specified message.
trans-unit.target: -O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageBinding%2A>método retorna a associação de mensagem para a mensagem especificada.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageBinding%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageDescription%2A> method returns the message for the specified message binding.
trans-unit.target: -O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageDescription%2A>método retorna a mensagem para a associação de mensagem especificada.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetMessageDescription%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationBinding%2A> method returns the operation binding for the specified operation.
trans-unit.target: -O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationBinding%2A>método retorna a associação da operação para a operação especificada.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationBinding%2A>

trans-unit.source: - The <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationDescription%2A> method returns the operation for the specified operation binding.
trans-unit.target: -O <xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationDescription%2A>método retorna a operação para a associação da operação especificada.</xref:System.ServiceModel.Description.WsdlEndpointConversionContext.GetOperationDescription%2A>
